{
  "text": "\u2022 Changing patient expectations, for example, in relation to antibiotic prescribing in upper respiratory infections, is potentially worthwhile, [CITATION_1] but may be challenging to implement and may achieve only modest change in practice. [CITATION_2] \u2022 Moving from a culture of medical dependency -'a pill for every ill' -to improved self-care utilising a range of formal and informal community-based resources is likely to be of importance in moderating demand for health care.",
